**Dark mode overrides** (add inside the existing `@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark)` block at line 38):
```css
.treemap-node {
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
}
.treemap-node:hover {
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
}
.treemap-group {
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
