```

#### 2. HTML — Add button bar containers (~lines 267-285)

Add a `<div class="entity-list-actions">` with "All" and "Clear" buttons inside each `.entity-list` div, BEFORE the dynamically-generated checkbox labels:

For Implementations tab (inside `#impls-list`):
```html
<div class="entity-list" id="impls-list">
  <div class="entity-list-actions">
    <button id="impls-all" title="Select all implementations">All</button>
